  "name": "Twisted Cloak, Stage 3",
  "type": "feat",
  "_id": "2rqKLtvrwVmxo1b9",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Jinchuuriki.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at <strong>4th level</strong> in this class mod, you have teetered on the edge of oblivion. You gain access to the <strong>Penultimate level</strong> of your <strong>Twisted Chakra Cloak</strong>. Your <strong>Twisted Cloak</strong> begins to bleed as it tears the skin from your flesh, leaving behind muscle and bone. You are but a few steps away from fully devolving into the beast within.</p><p>As a <strong>Bonus Action</strong>, while you are under the effects of <strong>Desperate Rage</strong> or <strong>Controlled Rage</strong> and have a <strong>Twisted Chakra pool</strong> of at least <strong>400 Twisted Chakra</strong>, you may spend <strong>90 Twisted Chakra</strong> to enter this <strong>Twisted Chakra Cloak Stage</strong>, gaining the following benefits:</p><ul><li>Your <strong>Speed</strong> is increased by <strong>60</strong>.</li><li>Your <strong>Strength</strong> and <strong>Dexterity</strong> increase by <strong>+4</strong>.</li><li>You gain a <strong>+4 Bonus</strong> to all <strong>Saving Throws</strong>.</li><li>As an <strong>Action</strong>, you can make <strong>2 Vermilion Attacks</strong> dealing <strong>5d8 + Proficiency</strong> Bludgeoning, Piercing, or Slashing damage (DM Discretion) using claws made of chakra.</li><li>You gain a <strong>+6 bonus</strong> to your <strong>Vermilion Attack Bonus</strong> and <strong>Vermilion Save DC</strong>.</li><li>Your <strong>melee attacks</strong> increase their range by <strong>20 feet</strong>.</li><li>You gain <strong>100 Twisted Hit Points</strong>.</li><li>You gain <strong>resistance</strong> to <strong>Slashing, Piercing, and Bludgeoning</strong> damage.</li><li>You regain <strong>15 Hit Points</strong> at the start of your turn.</li><li>You can cast <strong>Tier 3 Vermilion Art Techniques</strong>.</li><li>While in this <strong>Twisted Chakra Cloak</strong> Stage, your <strong>Desperate Rage DC</strong> increases by 2.</li></ul>",
      "chat": ""
